Prerequisite to setup the project:
run command: 'npm i' to install all the dependencies
Run 'db_schema.sql' on your machine to setup the database
Set environment variables according to your machine

To run the project in development environment-
'npm run dev'
For production environment-
'npm run start'

These are the environment variables required-
PORT
DB_HOST
DB_USER
DB_PASSWORD
DB_NAME=dbms_ecommerce
JWT_SECRET
JWT_EXPIRES
NODE_ENV
INTERNAL_API_KEY (only useful if you want to create admin)